title: Available Studio 1 Bath
posting_body: ['Austin, 78722', 'Manor Rd', '$2257', 'Studio', 'This apartment has wood-style floor in the living area and the kitchen, carpet in the bedroom(s), and tile in the bathroom(s).', 'The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, quartz counter-tops, and a dishwasher.', 'There is central AC and heat, in-unit laundry, and outside there is a patio/balcony.', 'Unit amenities include lighting fixtures, window coverings, and ceiling fans.', 'Wheelchair access.', 'Community amenities include pool, fitness center, clubhouse, package receiving, on-site management, storage, on-site maintenance, night patrol, elevator, business center, TV resident lounge, outdoor yoga space, BBQ grills, bike storage, and bike paths.', 'Pets welcome.', 'Off-street parking available and garage parking for additional monthly fee.', 'A four minute drive to Interstate 35.', 'Short term lease options.', 'PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT MAY VARY.', '***Availability and pricing is real-time, can change daily, and varies by lease term***', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
